description: The 46-year-old regularly posts pictures of herself at ITN's Central London studios, and last month she wore a black evening dress for a selfie in what she described only as a 'different' loo.

title: Del Boy actor Sir David Jason urges MPs to ban safari hunters' trophies
description: The Only Fools and Horses star, 82, has sent a letter to all MPs asking them to vote in favour of a Bill by Tory backbencher Henry Smith which would outlaw the cruel practice.
